Package ca.on.oicr.gsi.shesmu.plugin.types

Class GenericTypeGuarantee<T>

java.lang.Object
ca.on.oicr.gsi.shesmu.plugin.types.GenericTypeGuarantee<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the Java type being exported to Shesmu
Direct Known Subclasses:
TypeGuarantee
public abstract class GenericTypeGuarantee<T> extends Object
Matches to make Java's type checking produce correct types in Shesmu and can include generic types
